com.interpss.se.record

Interface SEBusRecord

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SEBaseRecord
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SEBusRecordImpl

    public interface SEBusRecord
extends SEBaseRecord
    A representation of the model object 'SE Bus Record'. SE Bus class

    The following features are supported:

    • Inject Value
    • JMatrix Index
    • All On Status
    See Also:
    SERecordPackage.getSEBusRecord()
